# ==============================================================================
# Trivy Security Scan Ignore List
# ==============================================================================

# AWS-0039: EKS cluster resources should have the encryption_config block set.
# Reason: KMS encryption config is intentionally omitted in the standalone EKS Auto Mode demo stack to simplify provisioning.
AWS-0039

# AWS-0040: Public EKS cluster access is enabled.
# Reason: Public API endpoints are required to allow developers and GitHub Actions runners to manage resources via kubectl.
AWS-0040

# AWS-0041: EKS Cluster allows access from a public CIDR: 0.0.0.0/0.
# Reason: Required for dynamic public access from dynamic GitHub Actions runner IPs.
AWS-0041

# AWS-0164: Subnet associates public IP address (map_public_ip_on_launch = true).
# Reason: Necessary for hosting external load balancers (ALB) and public-facing endpoints.
AWS-0164
